<p>Thinking about Itsuki Imazaki's episode in I Can't Understand What My Husband Is Saying S2.<br>
<br>
May be one of my favorite episodes ever done by him. So incredibly stylish and unique, it caught me off guard the first time I've seen the show, due to how it stands out.</p>
